::CyberShark::

    He smiled at Battera's words. He knew that is would be impossible for her 
to pick him up, but hey he did like the water.
    "Do you swim? I'd like to go down to the ocean, I haven't been in beast 
mode for a really long time." He asked her, he really hoped she did swim.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
::Magmatron::

    He found the Destrocons.
    "Greetings, Destrocons. I am Commander Magmatron of the Destrons," 
Magmatron said to them. "I wish to welcome you to my base."
    He saw three new Dinosaur modes a Dimorphodon, Pterodactyl, and a 
Quetsocoatylus. Part of his body.
    "How interesting, terosaurs." He said seeing them all. (BTW are they in 
Beast or Robot mode?)
